$$
\begin{align*}
\sum F_x &amp;= F_{k_1} + F_{N_2} - F_{a_x}\\
&amp;= - k_1(1-\cos \theta) L + N_2 - \frac {1}{2} m L \left(\ddot \theta \sin \theta+ \dot \theta ^2 \cos \theta \right)\\
&amp;= 0 \\
\sum F_y &amp;= F_{k_2} + F_{N_1} + G - F_{a_y} \\
&amp;= - k_2 L \sin \theta - N_1 + mg - \frac {1}{2} m L(\ddot \theta \cos \theta -\dot \theta ^2 \sin \theta )\\
&amp;= 0 \\
\sum M_O &amp;= M_{k_1} + M_{N_1} + M_{k_2} + M_{N_2}-M_\theta \\
&amp;= k_1(\cos \theta-1) L (\frac{L}{2} \sin \theta) + N_1(\frac{L}{2}\cos \theta) - k_2 L \sin \theta (\frac{L}{2} \cos \theta) - N_2 (\frac{L}{2} \sin \theta) -\frac{1}{12} m L^2 \ddot \theta \\
&amp;= 0
\end{align*}
$$

联立解得

$$
2 L m \ddot \theta +k_1 (6 L \sin \theta -3 L \sin 2 \theta)+3 k_2 L \sin 2 \theta -3 mg \cos \theta = 0
$$

div.data-content:
### 1)



$$
\begin{align*}
\delta W &= \sum F \delta r \\
&=F_{k_1} \delta r_1 + F_{k_2} \delta r_2 + G \delta r_g \\
&= -k_1 L(1-\cos \theta) \sin \theta \delta \theta - k_2 L \sin \theta \cos \theta \delta \theta + mg (\frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta ) \delta \theta \\
&= (\frac{1}{2} m g \cos \theta - k_1 \sin \theta + \frac { k_1 - k_2 } {2} \sin 2 \theta ) L \: \delta \theta \\
&= 0
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\Rightarrow \frac{1}{2} m g \cos \theta - k_1 \sin \theta + \frac { k_1 - k_2 } {2} \sin 2 \theta = 0
$$

\begin{cases}
F_{k_1} &= - k_1 \Delta x_1 \\
\Delta x_1 &= L - L \cos \theta \\
r_1 &= \Delta x_1\\
F_{k_2} &= -k_2 \Delta y_2 \\
\Delta y_2 &= L \sin \theta \\
r_2 &= \Delta x_2\\
G &= mg \\
r_g &= \frac{1}{2} L \sin \theta
\end{cases}
$$

div.data-content:
### 2)



$$
\begin{align*}
\sum F_x &= F_{k_1} + F_{N_2} - F_{a_x}\\
&= - k_1(1-\cos \theta) L + N_2 - \frac {1}{2} m L \left(\ddot \theta \sin \theta+ \dot \theta ^2 \cos \theta \right)\\
&= 0 \\
\sum F_y &= F_{k_2} + F_{N_1} + G - F_{a_y} \\
&= - k_2 L \sin \theta - N_1 + mg - \frac {1}{2} m L(\ddot \theta \cos \theta -\dot \theta ^2 \sin \theta )\\
&= 0 \\
\sum M_O &= M_{k_1} + M_{N_1} + M_{k_2} + M_{N_2}-M_\theta \\
&= k_1(\cos \theta-1) L (\frac{L}{2} \sin \theta) + N_1(\frac{L}{2}\cos \theta) - k_2 L \sin \theta (\frac{L}{2} \cos \theta) - N_2 (\frac{L}{2} \sin \theta) -\frac{1}{12} m L^2 \ddot \theta \\
&= 0
\end{align*}
$$

联立解得

$$
2 L m \ddot \theta +k_1 (6 L \sin \theta -3 L \sin 2 \theta)+3 k_2 L \sin 2 \theta -3 mg \cos \theta = 0
$$

$$

F_{k_2} &= -k_2 \Delta y_2 \\
\Delta y_2 &= L \sin \theta \\
G &= mg \\
F_{a_x} &= m \ddot x \\
x &= \Delta x_1 + \frac {1}{2} L \cos \theta\\
F_{a_y} &= m \ddot y \\
y &= \frac {1}{2}\Delta y_2 \\
M_\theta &= J \ddot \theta \\
J &= \frac{1}{3} m (\frac {L}{2})^2 \\
M_{k_1} &= - | F_{k_1} | (\frac{1}{2} L \sin \theta) \\
M_{N_1} &= N_1 (\frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta) \\
M_{k_2} &= - | F_{k_2} | (\frac{1}{2} L \cos \theta) \\
M_{N_2} &= - N_2 (\frac{1}{2} L \sin \theta)
\end{cases}
$$
